      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 24 初九</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 24 初九</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初九：不復遠，无只悔，元吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first NINE, undivided, shows its subject returning (from an error) of no great extent, which would not proceed to anything requiring repentance. There will be great good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
